Package org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage

Class OnlineIndexUpdates

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage.OnlineIndexUpdates
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterable<IndexEntryUpdate<IndexDescriptor>>, IndexUpdates
    public class OnlineIndexUpdates
extends Object
implements IndexUpdates
    Derives logical index updates from physical records, provided by node commands, relationship commands and property commands. For some types of updates state from store is also needed, for example if adding a label to a node which already has properties matching existing and online indexes; in that case the properties for that node needs to be read from store since the commands in that transaction cannot itself provide enough information. One instance can be fed data about multiple transactions, to be accessed later.
